5 (p)[(16)] Knowingly and willfully failing to comply with[ the provisions of] KRS
6 304.17A-714 when collecting claim overpayments from providers; or
7 (q)[(17)] Knowingly and willfully failing to comply with[ the provisions of] KRS
8 304.17A-708 on resolution of payment errors and retroactive denial of claims.
9 (2) An action shall not be brought against an insurer by a third-party claimant for a
